    map + <C-W>+
    map - <C-W>-
endif

" Move a line of text using Shift+[jk]
nmap <S-j> mz:m+<cr>`z
nmap <S-k> mz:m-2<cr>`z
vmap <S-j> :m'>+<cr>`<my`>mzgv`yo`z
vmap <S-k> :m'<-2<cr>`>my`<mzgv`yo`z

